INSERT INTO `articles` VALUES (23,'2009-01-16 22:32:37','Welcome to Xoundboy.com','<p>Hello and welcome to Xoundboy.com</p>\r\n<p>Please take a little time to have a look around, listen to some music and read about me and my work. If you like what you see and would like to be kept up to date then please <a href=\"cf_public/mailListFormP.cfm\"><u>join the mailing list</u> </a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Here, you will find an online catalogue of sound recordings made by myself, Ben Roberts a musician, sound engineer and music producer from Nottingham, UK. including some of <a href=\"http://www.xoundboy.com/xoundboy_nu_3/cf_public/artistDetailsP.cfm?actID=2\"> <u>my own stuff.</u></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Also, you will find a <a href=\"cf_public/gallery.cfm\"><u>gallery</u></a> of photographs taken by my girlfriend, a Czech photographer named Petra Lapkova, during our year-off travelling around South America from June \'06 - June \'07</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>On the <a href=\"cf_public/artists.cfm\"><u>artists</u></a> page you can listen to music that I have been working on over the past two or three years with several different artists.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Buried within the <a href=\"cf_public/recSearchP.cfm\"><u>recordings</u></a> page you can find and listen to nearly all of the finished (and some unfinished) work that I have been involved with over the years including the many recordings I made for the young un-signed artists of Manchester whilst working at Gorse Hill Studios.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Meanwhile in the <a href=\"html_files/projects.html\"><u>projects</u></a> page you can read about some of the various and diverse projects I have been involved with during my 14 year career in sound and music production.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>In the <a href=\"html_files/travels.html\"><u>travels</u></a> page you can track our progress so far around South America, see montages of travel photos and read about our experiences. Also, from time to time during the past months travelling we have come across interesting music that I have recorded, mixed and put up here for your listening pleasure.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" class=\"map_labels\">If you don\'t already have Adobe Flash Player Plugin installed then you will need to download and install it in order to listen to the mp3s on this site.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" class=\"map_labels\">Click <a href=\"http://www.adobe.com/shockwave/download/download.cgi?P1_Prod_Version=ShockwaveFlash\"><u>here</u></a> to go to the Flash player download site.</p>',00000946,NULL,'right','The original radio design','no','yes',2,2,0,'html_files/about.html','yes',0),(9,'2009-05-18 15:34:54','Petra is Gorgeous','<p>it\'s a fact and that\'s the truth. If anyone dares to dispute this then they will have to deal with me, Ben Roberts, the master hamster.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit, sed diam nonummy nibh euismod tincidunt ut laoreet dolore magna aliquam erat volutpat. Ut wisi enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exerci tation ullamcorper suscipit lobortis nisl ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis autem vel eum iriure dolor in hendrerit in vulputate velit esse molestie consequat, vel illum dolore eu feugiat nulla facilisis at vero eros et accumsan et iusto odio dignissim qui blandit praesent luptatum zzril delenit augue duis dolore te feugait nulla facilisi.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: arial black; font-size: medium;\">Lorem ipsum dolor s<a href=\"http://127.0.0.1:8500/CFIDE/administrator/\">it amet,</a> consectetuer adipiscing elit, sed diam nonummy nibh euismod tincidunt ut laoreet dolore magna aliquam erat volutpat. Ut wisi enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exerci tation ullamcorper suscipit lobortis nisl ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis autem vel eum iriure dolor in hendrerit in vulputate velit esse molestie consequat, vel illum dolore eu feu</span>giat nulla fac