nes you buy cream cakes in) and held together with about 100 miles of selotape. Recordings were made of the sounds made by paper bags being ripped. The consequenting piece of music was assembled using these sounds plus a few others recorded at a \"Paper Bag Party\" that took place on board the Fitzcarraldo theatre ship, moored in Salford Quays. Dancers moved around the inflatable space to the music to complete a strange, yet powerful ensemble.','yes','Paperbagmusic','','0'),(356,00002,'Packing Up',4198392,77,'Gorse Hill Studios','2000-12-24 00:00:00',00012,462,'One of the first finished tracks to be made at Gorse Hill Studios after it first opened.','yes','Packing Up','','0'),(462,00002,'The Club',2305003,83,'Gorse Hill Studios','2003-12-30 00:00:00',00012,462,'','yes','The Club','','0'),(463,00002,'The Hustle Game',5464932,83,'Gorse Hill Studios','2003-12-30 00:00:00',00012,462,'','yes','The Hustle Game','','0'),(354,00002,'Out of the Blue',0,76,'Martin Cooper\'s Studio, Attenborough, Notts','1994-12-24 00:00:00',00001,465,'Last Track on 1994 Album \"Paris or New Orleans\" by Egomania','yes','Out of the Blue','','0'),(353,00003,'Otis',8192567,27,'The Bridgewater Hall, Manchester','2004-09-16 00:00:00',00017,470,'http://www.cerysmaticfactory.info/durutti-bridgewater-hall-160904.html','no','Otis','','0'),(352,00010,'Only The Now',3511753,2,'The Chapel, Penisarwyn, Snowdonia, Wales','2004-11-24 00:00:00',00006,378,'my first attempt at writing string arrangements using sampled violins and cellos.','yes','Only The Now','','0'),(351,00002,'On the up',5347845,2,'Studio 8, Chorlton, Manchester','2005-09-24 00:00:00',00006,378,'An instrumental bavking track put together for Helen Derridge but never used.','yes','On the up','','0'),(350,00002,'Now We\'re Letting Go',4118986,44,'Manchester, UK','2005-03-24 00:00:00',00012,960,'','yes','Now We\'re Letting Go','','0'),(349,00002,'Not Cool Enough',8426984,75,'Gorse Hill Studios','2004-12-24 00:00:00',00012,462,'','yes','Not Cool